                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971025-1-defend54 t17971025-1-punish6"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 26.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
